Guru: MySQL Cluster
Mark Matthews, Software Dev Manager, MySQL AB
Guru: Connector/J, JDBC, Java
Peter Gulutzan, Software Architect, MySQL AB
Guru: ストアード・プロシージャー, SQL 標準
Elliot Murphy, Lead Replication Developer, MySQL AB
Guru: Replication
Michael Zinner, Lead Tools Developer, MySQL AB
Guru: MySQL Administrator, Query Browser, Migration Toolkit

